              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium mb-2" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.1); color: var(--color-primary-400);">Audit began Q1 2026</span>
              <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: #b8c3c7;">SOC 2 Type I audit covering Security, Availability, and Confidentiality trust service criteria. Report expected Q2 2026.</p>
